{{Quote|This is Hammer 3:2. We require a tech team up here as quickly as possible. Nothing major, but our port repulsors need looking at.|Sergeant Arbmab|<ref name="The Assault on Protazk">{{WEGCite|story=The Assault on Protazk|book=Imperial Sourcebook|reprint=1}}</ref>}}
'''Hammer 3:2''' was a [[S-1 FireHawke Heavy Repulsortank]] in the [[Imperial Hammers Elite Armor Unit/Legends|Imperial Hammers Elite Armor Unit]]. During the [[Assault on Protazk|assault]] on [[Protazk]], its crew included [[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] [[Arbmab/Legends|Arbmab]] and [[Gortz]].

